{"lemma":"مُخَلَّفاتٌ","slug":"مُخَلَّفاتٌ","root":"خ.ل.ف","root_slug":"خ-ل-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ل-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مُخَلَّف","root":"خلف","pos":"N","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11370","n11371","n11372"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%AE%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11370","headword_ar":"مَخْلَفٌ","root":"xlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxolafapN","text_ar":"مَخْلَفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n11371","headword_ar":"مُخْلِفٌ","root":"xlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has exceeded in age the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAzil","text_ar":"بَازِل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [which latter is generally"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one that has entered the ninth year;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, M, K;) beyond which there is no age [having an epithet to denote it]; therefore, (TA,) one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxolifu EaAmK","text_ar":"مُخْلِفُ عَامٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxolifu","text_ar":"مُخْلِفُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmayoni","text_ar":"عَامَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has exceeded in age the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAzl","text_ar":"بازل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by a year"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by two years"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, TA; [see 4;]) applied alike to the male and the female; (S, K;) and the female is also termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxolafapN","text_ar":"مُخْلَفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or this latter signifies (tropical:)  a she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that appears,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is thought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be pregnant, and is not pregnant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K:) and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxaAliyfu","text_ar":"مَخَالِيفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mixolaAfN","text_ar":"مِخْلَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  Also A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose cattle have not obtained the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabiyE","text_ar":"رَبِيع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (JK.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN muxolifN mutolifN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ مُخْلِفٌ مُتْلِفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mixolafN","text_ar":"مِخْلَفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mitolafN","text_ar":"مِتْلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mitolaAfN","text_ar":"مِتْلَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mixolaAfN","text_ar":"مِخْلَافٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tlf","text_ar":"تلف"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawomapu AlD~uHaY muxolifapN lilofami","text_ar":"نَوْمَةُ الضُّحَى مُخْلِفَةٌ لِلْفَمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) also written ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxolafapN","text_ar":"مَخْلَفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and in some copies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawomu AlD~uHaY","text_ar":"نَوْمُ الضُّحَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which requires the reading"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxolafapN","text_ar":"مَخْلَفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (TA,) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sleep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sleeping, in the period of the morning when the sun is yet low is"},{"kind":"text","text":"] a cause of the mouth's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"becoming altered"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the worse"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in odour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxolifu janobK","text_ar":"مُخْلِفُ جَنْبٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having one half of his face and of his mouth turning sideways."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.) ―         -b7-  See also the explanation of the verse of El- Hoteiäh cited in the last quarter of the first paragraph. The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTaA","text_ar":"قَطَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxolifaAtN","text_ar":"مُخْلِفَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"because they draw water for their young ones. (JK.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","K","S","A"]},{"entry_id":"n11372","headword_ar":"مِخْلَفٌ","root":"xlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}